Feature Your Old ACI Setup New ACA + Browserless Setup
Start Time 60 - 90 seconds < 1 second
Concurrency 1 user per ACI 10+ users per Container
VNC Setup Manual Xvfb/noVNC/Caddy Built-in to Browserless
Cost Cheap (Pay per run) Moderate (Pay for 1 idle instance)
Scaling Manual/Scripted Automatic (KEDA)
